Package edu.kit.kastel.sdq.featuremodel.provider

Class FeaturemodelItemProviderAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.AdapterFactoryImpl
      • edu.kit.kastel.sdq.featuremodel.util.FeaturemodelAdapterFactory
        • edu.kit.kastel.sdq.featuremodel.provider.FeaturemodelItemProviderAdapterFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AdapterFactory, ComposeableAdapterFactory, IChangeNotifier, IDisposable
    public class FeaturemodelItemProviderAdapterFactory
extends FeaturemodelAdapterFactory
implements ComposeableAdapterFactory, IChangeNotifier, IDisposable
    This is the factory that is used to provide the interfaces needed to support Viewers. The adapters generated by this factory convert EMF adapter notifications into calls to fireNotifyChanged. The adapters also support Eclipse property sheets. Note that most of the adapters are shared among multiple instances.
    Generated class or method.
